(upbeat music)

41
00:01:16.020 --> 00:01:18.720
Artists who lent their talents to the cause.

42
00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:19.590
Local celebrities-

43
00:01:19.590 --> 00:01:20.520
<v ->Brad Evans here.</v>

44
00:01:20.520 --> 00:01:21.353
<v ->What's up, y'all?</v>

45
00:01:21.353 --> 00:01:23.250
It's Doug.
<v ->who shared on social.</v>

46
