And even the mayor got on board.

47
00:01:24.750 --> 00:01:27.570 line:15% 
<v ->I hereby proclaim November 24th, 2023,</v>

48
00:01:27.570 --> 00:01:29.400 line:15% 
to be Black Black Friday.

49
00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:30.510
<v Narrator>And all that work paid off</v>

50
00:01:30.510 --> 00:01:32.460
for the people who matter most.

51
00:01:32.460 --> 00:01:36.330
<v ->To be seen outside of just your community means a lot.</v>

52
00:01:36.330 --> 00:01:38.700
<v ->Business owners that I've been in communication with</v>

53
00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:41.357
have all realized increased sales.

54
00:01:41.357 --> 00:01:45.030
<v ->We were, you know, up close to 60% of new customers.</v>

55
00:01:45.030 --> 00:01:47.310
<v ->Yeah, every day is Black Black Friday now.</v>

56
00:01:47.310 --> 00:01:50.310
<v Narrator>So yeah, our little movement made a big impact,</v>

57
00:01:50.310 --> 00:01:53.310
put money back in the pockets of Black business owners,

58
00:01:53.310 --> 00:01:55.590
and got the people talking in a big way.

59
00:01:55.590 --> 00:01:56.910
But if you ask us,

60
00:01:56.910 --> 00:01:59.433
the real impact has only just begun.

